title: A New Day's Hurry (Farming & Cozy & New Settlement OST)
description: A New Day's Hurry is a 10 track farming/cozy vibes/new settlement themed album mainly inspired by the famous games in the genre.
longDescription:
A New Day's Hurry is a 10 track farming, cozy vibes, new settlement themed album; mainly inspired by the famous games in the genre, featuring ukulele and other similar type of world instruments.


Album trailer can be listened on Youtube by following this link.


This album is made of:

  • 3 General BGM Music That Can Be Played During Any Moment In The Game
  • 1 Discovery Song
  • 2 Activity Songs (Farming and Fishing)
  • 2 Location Themes (Pub and Museum)
  • 2 Dungeon Music


Total Album Duration: 22 Minutes

Can Be Edited or Remixed?: Yes

Attribution?: Not required

Does Loop?: No
